<section>
	<h2>Purpose</h2>
	<p>Add full-width bands to elements inside containers.</p>
</section>

<section class="alert alert-info">
	<h2>Note</h2>
	<p>The background-color needs to be added via other CSS classes, this plugin only sets the structure so that the element can span the full-width of the page.</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Example</h2>
	<div class="wb-band bg-primary">
		<section>
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="mrgn-tp-md">Inspired to create your own open data project?</h2>
				<p>Explore how Canadians are using open data to power innovation and its impact on communities.</p>
				<p><a class="btn btn-success" href="https://open.canada.ca/en/stories" role="button">Get started</a></p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>

	<section>
		<h3>Code</h3>
		<section>
			<h4>HTML</h4>
			<pre><code>&lt;div class=&quot;wb-band bg-primary&quot;&gt;
	&lt;section&gt;
		&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;
			&lt;h2 class=&quot;mrgn-tp-md&quot;&gt;Inspired to create your own open data project?&lt;/h2&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;Explore how Canadians are using open data to power innovation and its impact on communities.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;btn btn-success&quot; href=&quot;https://open.canada.ca/en/stories&quot; role=&quot;button&quot;&gt;Get started&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h4>CSS</h4>
			<pre><code>.wb-band {
	margin-left: 50%;
	transform: translateX(-50%);
	width: 100vw;
}
</code></pre>
		</section>
	</section>
</section>
